# Wiki Search Index

<!-- Agent-optimized search index. Match query terms against Tags and Key Terms columns,
     then read only matched pages. Updated on every ingest, code-commit, and lint operation.

     Maintenance rules:
     - New wiki page → add new row.
     - Page archived → update row with archive/ prefix.
     - Page NEVER deleted (always archive) → row never removed.
     - Parity with _INDEX.md checked during lint: every _INDEX entry must exist here and vice versa.

     Column rules:
     - Page: Obsidian wikilink (clickable)
     - Type: page type from _SCHEMA.md Section 2 (core, entity, concept, decision, insight, archive, source-summary)
     - Tags: copy of frontmatter tags field (comma-separated)
     - Key Terms: 5-15 search terms extracted from page content — technical concepts, technology names, IDs, domain terms
     - Summary: single line, max ~100 characters

     Details: _SCHEMA.md Section 13. -->

